# Production Recovery

- Check instance and network status before remediation actions.
- If app is down, follow this order:
  1. Check container/process status.
  2. Check service and proxy logs.
  3. Restart only affected services if required.
- Never redeploy blindly when root cause is unknown.
- Fix root cause before restart or redeploy.
- Verify recovery with endpoint checks and container health checks.
